<br>
I have gotten nearly all my dropped spells for 20-60pp each on Terris-Thule.  Someone threw T-Rod at me, for free cause they thought it was another 2HB weapon that sucked.  CoTH was sold to me for 30pp because I told the person it was the pet version.<br>
<br>
Voc Water, 60pp had a guildmate tell the seller &quot;good luck selling it, I have been here with 8 of them for weeks and can't sell them at 100pp&quot;. Then I asked the seller how much, they said 100pp, I replied, hmmmmmm I have 60pp on me.<br>
<br>
Gvoc Water, 200pp insisted that I needed it for a quest, and the spell really wasn't worth much, since I only had a 25% chance of getting what I wanted from the quest.  They sold me 3 for 600pp.<br>
<br>
Still looking for muzzle of Mardu though, and I have no clue what gimp line I am going to come up with for that one.  I'll probably bite the bullet for the muzzle and pay what it's worth.  Nice people really, they are willing to believe almost anything.  <br>
<br>
On the flip side, I was traveling with a druid companion one day and someone was begging for a port.  I recognised the name and asked druid if he would take the guy (we were going to the same ring anyway).  The druid agreed and the guy dropped 3 spells on the druid and asked if those would do.<br>
<br>
